              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Secondary protons were analyzed in",
                "momentum by a magnetic spectrometer with an",
                "acceptance angle +-0.5 degrees and were recorded by a",
                "spark chamber telescope. The polarization of the",
                "protons was determined by the asymmetry of their",
                "scattering in the spark chamber telescope. Events with",
                "stopping of a  proton in the spark chamber were",
                "recorded by coincidence of the pulses of two",
                "scintillation counters and anticoincidence of one",
                "scintillation counter."
              ]
            }
          ],
